Thanks for the feedback

I have fixed the things

Input section
* You do not need to give an example here.
* It is not "an array" separated by spaces. It is "an [[array]] of integers" separated by spaces. Please fix the wording.

Output section
* Please move the example to Goal section.

Constraints section
* Please format array as a [[variable]]. (both lines)

Cases
* In the cases "Big Validator 2", "The boss chonk of a test" and "Validator 5", some numbers are -50 and 50 and hence the case violates the second constraint, which states that they are strictly between -50 and 50 (both ends exclusive). Please fix the cases or the constraint.

Thanks.
